    USAGE INSTRUCTIONS:
    
    1. FLEXIBLE LENGTH: This template can be copied/extended for as many pages as needed
    2. PAGE BREAKS: Add <div class="page-break"></div> between pages as needed
    3. PROFESSIONAL FORMATTING: Maintains consistent typography and spacing
    4. WIDOW/ORPHAN CONTROL: CSS prevents awkward line breaks
    5. SECTION BREAKS: Use decorative breaks between major sections
    6. ENDNOTES: Properly formatted academic-style citations
    7. AVOID-BREAK CLASS: Use on elements that shouldn't split across pages
    
    FOR MULTI-PAGE CHAPTERS:
    - Copy this template for each content page
    - Update page numbers sequentially
    - Ensure endnotes only appear on the final content page
    - Use section breaks to create natural page divisions
